pl.sudokusolver.recognizerlib.sudoku

Class SudokuExtractor

  • java.lang.Object
    • pl.sudokusolver.recognizerlib.sudoku.SudokuExtractor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISudokuExtractor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BaseSudokuExtractor

    public abstract class SudokuExtractor
extends java.lang.Object
implements ISudokuExtractor
    This class connect all levels of extracting sudoku img in one abstract component.
    It contains all functionality to be able to control process of extraction.
